1001
01:30:05,400 --> 01:30:06,334
Don't worry about it.

1002
01:30:06,435 --> 01:30:07,470
Get your head into the fight.

1003
01:30:07,570 --> 01:30:08,804
That's Cupcake
Cassidy out there.

1004
01:30:08,904 --> 01:30:11,373
