1024
01:31:36,424 --> 01:31:37,526
Watch it.

1025
01:31:52,007 --> 01:31:52,908
Come on.

1026
01:32:02,017 --> 01:32:05,888
[cheering]

1027
01:32:42,357 --> 01:32:43,258
Come on!

1028
01:32:55,337 --> 01:32:56,238
