1029
01:32:56,338 --> 01:32:57,239
Hey, come on!

1030
01:32:57,339 --> 01:32:58,240
Come on!

1031
01:32:58,340 --> 01:33:00,242
Get over there!

1032
01:33:00,342 --> 01:33:04,212
